{# Park-minimal belief update — persona + memory + event → react.
   No psychological scaffolding beyond a single one-line "be honest" framing.
   The realism comes from rich persona + accumulated memory, not from
   prescribing how to think. #}

{% if reflections -%}
The general shape of how things have felt over the past years (you don't
remember the specifics, just the feeling):

{% for r in reflections -%}
[{{ r.timestamp }}] {{ r.content }}

{% endfor %}
{% endif -%}
{% if recent_memories -%}
Specific memories that are still vivid for you:

{% for m in recent_memories -%}
[{{ m.timestamp }}] {{ m.content }}

{% endfor %}
{% endif -%}
{% if not reflections and not recent_memories -%}
You haven't experienced anything specific yet beyond what shaped you up to
the start of 2020. Your priors come from your background.

{% endif -%}

──────────────────────────────────────────
IT IS NOW {{ event_date }}.
──────────────────────────────────────────

{% if first_appearance is defined and not first_appearance -%}
This is something that has been happening for a while now and is still going on:

**{{ event.headline }}**

{{ event.summary }}
{% else -%}
The following news event has reached you:

**{{ event.headline }}**

{{ event.summary }}
{% endif -%}

{% if event.party_direction_summary is defined and event.party_direction_summary -%}
({{ event.party_direction_summary }} You may agree or disagree with that read; what matters is how *you* take it.)

{% endif -%}
React in character. Be honest — most news doesn't change real people's minds. Only say something shifted if it genuinely would for *you*, given who you are and what you remember.

Output ONLY a JSON object (no preamble, no markdown fences):

```json
{
  "engagement": "scrolled_past" | "skimmed" | "engaged",
  "reaction": "ignored" | "noted_no_change" | "shifted_my_view",
  "monologue": "<2-4 first-person sentences if you reacted; null if you scrolled past>",
  "importance": <integer 1-10, how much this matters to your worldview>,
  "structured_delta": {
    "party_lean_change": "more_BJP" | "more_AITC" | "more_LeftINC" | "more_Other" | "no_change",
    "salience_added": ["<topic>", ...],
    "trust_changes": {"<entity>": "+small" | "+large" | "-small" | "-large"}
  }
}
```
